quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  104,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  104,1,tabahi hai har uss shakhs ke liye jo ( mun Dur mun ) logon par ta'an aur ( peeth peechay ) buraiyan karne ka khogar hai
  104,2,jis ne maal jama kya aur ussay gun gun kar rakha
  104,3,woh samjhta hai ke uss ka maal hamesha uss ke paas rahay ga
  104,4,"hargiz nahi, woh shakhs to chikna chor kar dainay wali jagah mein pheink diya jaye ga"
  104,5,aur tum kya jano ke kya hai woh chikna chor kar dainay wali jagah ?
  104,6,"Allah ki aag, khoob bharkayi hui"
  104,7,jo dilon taq puhanche gi
  104,8,woh unn par dhaank kar band kar di jaye gi
  104,9,( iss haalat mein ke woh ) ounchay ounchay satonon mein ( ghiry hue hon ge )
